    "display_name": "Create a Comic or Joke",
    "long_instructions": "## Create a Comic or Joke\r\n\r\n\r\n**Before You Start:**\r\n\r\nMake sure you have filled in the **K** and **W** columns of your KWL chart for this task.\r\n\r\n**Do:**\r\n\r\nAsk AI to write a short comic strip idea or joke based on a school-related topic.\r\n\r\n**Try:**\r\n\r\nAsk for different formats-like a knock-knock joke, a 3-panel comic, or something pun-based.\r\n\r\n**Check:**\r\n\r\nIs it actually funny? Does the humor make sense and fit your topic?\r\n\r\n**After You Try It:**\r\n\r\n1. Fill in the **L** column of your KWL chart\r\n2. Press **Continue** to return to the task menu\r\n",
